[size=5][b]InGame Info [color=#ff0000]XML[/color][/b] (+[b][color=#ff0000]Text[/color][/b] +[b][color=#ff0000]JSON[/color][/b])[/size]
Display various information directly only you ingame screen.


[b]Note[/b]
This mod is a fork of [url=http://www.minecraftforum.net/topic/1009577-]bspkrs' version[/url] which he keeps updated with all Minecraft versions past 1.0 (the original author of the mod is DaftPVF).
As of version 2.4.1.[b]27[/b] InGame Info XML supports bspkrs' [b]text format[/b], however there are a few things that have to be adjusted for it to work as you're used to.
[list]
[*]Color codes (&f, &a, &r) have to use the [b]$[/b] symbol instead of the [b]&[/b] symbol (&f => $f, &a => $r, ...).
[*]The syntax for boolean tags (slimes, daytime, raining, ...; check the download page for a list of all tags) has changed a bit.
Example: The slime tag would have to be modified from the following
[code]<slimes[yes/no]>[/code]
to the following
[code]<if[slimes[yes/no]]>[/code]
[/list]


[b]Authors[/b] (in chronological order)
DaftPVF (latest update for 1.0 - [url=http://www.minecraftforum.net/topic/124117-]click![/url])
bspkrs (latest update for 1.6.4, simple text syntax - [url=http://www.minecraftforum.net/topic/1009577-]click![/url])
