[size=5][b]DynIMC[/b][/size]
This mod allows the user to send custom IMC messages to mods. This is particularly useful when trying to add support for mod A to mod B (for example, adding axes/shears from Redstone Arsenal to Treecapitator).

[b]Note:[/b] this mod requires you to know whether a mod has an IMC API and what it looks like. You can find examples for Treecapitator and Thermal Expansion 3 on the wiki. I will [b]try[/b] to keep that list up to date as people notify me of IMC APIs.


